─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Data Notice
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
The pretrained model weights released with this repository were trained on data
from the Alzheimer's Disease Neuroimaging Initiative (ADNI). ADNI data are
subject to the ADNI Data Use Agreement (https://adni.loni.usc.edu).
Preprocessed ADNI data embeddings are NOT redistributed in this repository.
Users must independently obtain ADNI data access through the official portal.
